==============================================================================
COMMANDS                                                   *redacted-commands*

:Redact                                                              *:Redact*
-------
Redact some text.

:Redact!                                                            *:Redact!*
--------
Clear all redacted text.

:RedactedW                                                        *:RedactedW*
--------
Persist Redacted's highlighting, so your file will still look the same if you
close it and open it again.


==============================================================================
MAPPINGS                                                   *redacted-mappings*

<Plug>Redact                                                    *<Plug>Redact*
------------
In normal mode it works as an operator, in visual mode it just redacts the
text in the visual selection.


==============================================================================
FUNCTIONS                                                 *redacted-functions*

Redact('pattern')                                                     *Redact()*
------------
Use `call Redact('pattern')` to redact all text matching the specified regex
pattern.


